      <title>自12月以来，美国抵押贷款利率下降了第六周至最低</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-03-12/us-mortgage-rates-drop-for-a-sixth-week-to-lowest-since-december</link>
      <description><![CDATA[自12月初以来，美国平均30年抵押贷款率连续第六周下降到最低水平，从而引发了购买和再融资活动的收集。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-03-12/us-mortgage-rates-drop-for-a-sixth-week-to-lowest-since-december</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 12 Mar 2025 11:00:00 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>印度通货膨胀进一步缓解，提高利率降低了希望</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-03-12/india-inflation-eases-further-boosting-rate-cut-hopes</link>
      <description><![CDATA[印度的通货膨胀率在2月的七个月低至7个月，与中央银行的目标保持一致，并提高了进一步降低利率的希望。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-03-12/india-inflation-eases-further-boosting-rate-cut-hopes</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 12 Mar 2025 10:36:03 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>美国财政投资者驳回了通货膨胀，因为增长的恐惧占主导地位</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-03-12/us-traders-look-blase-about-inflation-as-growth-angst-dominates</link>
      <description><![CDATA[国库市场的投资者在周三关于美国通货膨胀的关键报告之前的价格压力令人惊讶地毫不关心，而是专注于美国增长的前景。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-03-12/us-traders-look-blase-about-inflation-as-growth-angst-dominates</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 12 Mar 2025 10:11:32 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>2月CPI报告的期望</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/videos/2025-03-12/what-to-expect-from-february-s-cpi-report</link>
      <description><![CDATA[预计美国CPI的报告显示，在较高的食品价格上，核心通货膨胀率在2月上涨了0.3％，在年初上涨0.5％之后。迈克尔·麦基（Michael McKee）在彭博电视台（Bloomberg Television）进行了预览。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/videos/2025-03-12/what-to-expect-from-february-s-cpi-report</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 12 Mar 2025 10:03:23 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>流向印度股票资金缓慢，因为溃败在情绪上</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-03-12/flows-to-indian-stock-funds-slow-as-selloff-weighs-on-sentiment</link>
      <description><![CDATA[印度股票资金的流入在10个月内下降到最低，因为延长的市场低迷促使一些投资者推迟新的曝光率。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-03-12/flows-to-indian-stock-funds-slow-as-selloff-weighs-on-sentiment</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 12 Mar 2025 07:58:20 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
